        </p>
        <p>
            I value transparency in both teamwork and technology. I am especially
            interested in open-source projects and in building software that promotes
            free access to knowledge, collaboration, and shared growth within the
            developer community.
        </p>
        <p>
            I believe software should be understandable, reusable, and accessible,
            and I aim to apply these principles in both academic and professional
            projects.
        </p>
    </section>
    <Education />
    <Experience />
    <section class="container">
        <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
        <TechStack />
    </section>
    <Certifications />
    <section id="projects" class="container">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            {projects.map(p => <ProjectCard project={p} />)}
